{"tid":1065791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑似拐子佬現身九龍灣 $200利誘女童食晚飯","createTime":"2019-03-17T13:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T01:51:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c8b0054ae4450285516d1de1582e65a23e18afe4","tid":1065791,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190317/large/1552827030_34f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190317%2Flarge%2F1552827030_34f8.jpg&h=6d050d7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九龍灣出現懷疑拐子佬！晚上7時許，一名年約10歲的女童於麗晶花園附近的宏光道休憩處嬉戲，突然有一名陌生男子上前搭訕，聲稱可用$200請女童食飯，女童立即將事件告知母親，母親覺得事態嚴重立即報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場調查，並在公園附近進行搜索，惟該男子已經離開，事後女童及其母親在警員的陪同下返回警署助查。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190317/59379743\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190317%2F59379743&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2F6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=e5716b14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190317%2F59379743&h=28e3c8eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190317/59379743</a>"},{"pid":"e92439e71acf68a3ebfb8a43f82d879cc81a83e3","tid":1065791,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:35:09.000Z","msg":"邊個連登會員自己認左佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4662a54b845234e5c8bd1427135402b852a16f","tid":1065791,"uid":37297,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:35:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J7pMnmq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ7pMnmq.jpg&h=875464e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84d65904b458539b7df1e15c0165930da0c068a6","tid":1065791,"uid